ov/lyft-uber-settlement"><ins>纽约总检察长的网站</ins></a>上提出索赔，要求获得自己应得的和解份额。这些公司还需要更新其应用程序，以改进提出病假申请的流程，并为与薪酬相关的问题提供支持，以及详细解释其薪酬的司机收益报表。</p><p>近年来，在<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/labor-department-biden-administration-gig-workers-employee-status-proposal-172219009.html"><ins>拜登政府推动</ins></a>将零工工人归类为雇员的背景下，纽约一直在打击基于应用程序的服务提供商。然而，加州一家法院<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/court-rules-uber-lyft-keep-contractors-classification-drivers-california-054040457.html"><ins>在三月份否决了一项此类法案</ins></a>，允许公司继续将其司机归类为承包商。但纽约州最近在确保更多保护方面取得了进展。 9 月，Uber、GrubHub 和 DoorDash 被告知必须<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/uber-grubhub-and-doordash-must-pay-nyc-delivery-workers-an-18-minimum-wage-213145847.html"><ins>向送货员支付最低工资</ins></a>。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/uber-and-lyft-must-pay-328-million-to-new-york-drivers-in-massive-wage-theft-settlement-155716817 .html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/uber-and-lyft-must-pay-328-million-to-new-york-drivers-in-massive-wage-theft-settlement-155716817.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9ec2f7c6-e214-4b29-ab71-71553dadd427</guid><dc:creator>夏安·麦克唐纳</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 15:57:16 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1698940637</ingested><modified> 2023-11-02T15:57:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Business]]></category><category><![CDATA[Employment & Career]]></category><category><![CDATA[Company Legal & Law Matters]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="2400" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-images/2020-01/a2a88640-30c7-11ea-bbef-e2cbfb324c9d" width="3606"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2400" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-images/2020-01/a2a88640-30c7-11ea-bbef-e2cbfb324c9d" width="3606"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Jefferson Siegel / Reuters]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An Uber car is pictured in New York City, New York, U.S., December 6, 2019. REUTERS/Jefferson Siegel]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[UBER-SAFETY/CONGRESS]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Listen to the 'final' Beatles song, 'Now and Then,' made with help from AI]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>披头士乐队好像又回来了。披头士四人组刚刚发行了一首新歌，这是该乐队自 1995 年以来的第一首歌曲。《Now and Then》被宣传为披头士乐队的最后一首歌曲，考虑到其中两名成员已经去世，而另外两名成员也已超过 80 岁，这是有道理的。</p><p>这首歌是使用约翰·列侬 (John Lennon) 1970 年代的演示曲目和乔治·哈里森 (George Harrison) 1995 年的吉他曲目创作的。幸存的披头士乐队成员保罗·麦卡特尼 (Paul McCartney) 和林戈·斯塔尔 (Ringo Starr) 在<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/paul-mccartney-is-using-ai-to-create-a-final-song-for-the-beatles-133839244.html">现代机器学习技术的帮助下完成了这首曲子。</a> </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="898e1f6a9d5646c499aceea8941aa197"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AW55J2zE3N4?si=BMluLzC40u3qd5SW" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>该软件首次由导演彼得·杰克逊在为苹果公司制作纪录片<em>《回归》</em>时使用，它能够将列侬的声音与钢琴声分开，没有任何出血，让剩下的披头士乐队可以自由发挥，添加他们想要的任何内容。您可以<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=APJAQoSCwuA">在这里观看有关这首歌制作的纪录片。</a></p><p>至于歌曲本身，这是一首相对缓慢的列侬民谣，他的声音是一大亮点。麦卡特尼轻松地写下一首贝斯线，斯塔尔则敲鼓。吉他独奏是哈里森的风格，但实际上并不是他演奏的，尽管他在背景中处理了一些节奏吉他。还有一个完整的管弦乐安排，因为，嗯，这是披头士乐队。这可能不会成为该乐队最受欢迎的曲目之一，但列侬的声音既令人难忘又美丽。</p><p> 《Now and Then》原定于 1995 年作为披头士乐队选集的一部分发行，另外两首歌曲《Free as a Bird》和《Real Love》是从 20 世纪 70 年代列侬小样中精选出来的。然而，早在 20 世纪 90 年代，还没有技术能够将列侬的声音与钢琴分开，同时又不会严重影响原始效果。</p><p>披头士乐队可能会说这是他们有史以来的最后一首歌，但我们将在 2053 年进行报道，看看这是否属实。回头见。与此同时，检查一下轨道。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/listen-to-the-final-beatles-track-made-with-machine-learning-and-archival-recordings-153253946.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/listen-to-the-final-beatles-track-made-with-machine-learning-and-archival-recordings-153253946.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 084b600a-3203-46e6-9b00-fa05f5d98251</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 15:32:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1698945815</ingested><modified> 2023-11-02T17:23:39+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Lifestyle]]></category><category><![CDATA[Music]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1532" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/95b0a800-7993-11ee-bf9f-65a1195885ee" width="2688"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1532" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/95b0a800-7993-11ee-bf9f-65a1195885ee" width="2688"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[The Beatles]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[The Beatles waving goodbye.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The Beatles]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[NASA is launching a free streaming service with live shows and original series]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> NASA 宣布推出一项名为<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.nasa.gov/plus/" data-original-link="https://www.nasa.gov/plus/">NASA+</a>的新流媒体服务，该服务将于下周登陆大多数主要平台。它将完全免费，没有订阅要求，并且您不会被迫观看广告。 NASA+ 将于 11 月 8 日开始提供。 </p><div id="3efb5da8775f4c90956ee70609bf3547"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们发射的不仅仅是火箭。本月，我们推出了新的流媒体服务 NASA+。 <a href="https://t.co/McWnWOKXSu">https://t.co/McWnWOKXSu</a><br><br>没有订阅要求。<br>无广告。免费。家庭友善！<br>荣获艾美奖的现场表演<br>原创系列<br>在大多数主要平台上<a href="https://t.co/5ffjptumUJ">pic.twitter.com/5ffjptumUJ</a></p> — 美国宇航局 (@NASA) <a href="https://twitter.com/NASA/status/1719823286194852289?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 11 月 1 日</a></blockquote></div><p>该<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.nasa.gov/news-release/nasa-launches-beta-site-on-demand-streaming-app-update-coming-soon/" data-original-link="https://www.nasa.gov/news-release/nasa-launches-beta-site-on-demand-streaming-app-update-coming-soon/">航天局</a>此前曾透露，将在今年夏天发布即将推出的流媒体服务，以更广泛地改进其数字业务。当时，它表示 NASA+ 将在 NASA iOS 和 Android 应用程序以及 Roku、Apple TV 和 Fire TV 等流媒体播放器上提供。您还可以在网络上观看。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>目前还没有关于内容本身的太多细节，但美国宇航局表示，其适合家庭的节目通过现场报道和原创视频系列“让您融入我们的任务”。 NASA 已经拥有自己的广播网络，称为 NASA TV，而新的流媒体服务似乎是其扩展。但是，当它下周三正式推出时，我们会了解更多信息。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nasa-is-launching-a-free-streaming-service-with-live-shows-and-original-series-150128180.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nasa-is-launching-a-free-streaming-service-with-live-shows-and-original-series-150128180.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f59faa85-e46b-404f-8282-7ba087129335</guid><dc:creator>夏安·麦克唐纳</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 15:01:28 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1698937289</ingested><modified> 2023-11-02T15:01:31+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Science]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Cheyenne MacDonald]]></category><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/8dae7910-798f-11ee-8ab7-eb5cc8b0026d" width="1280"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-11/8dae7910-798f-11ee-8ab7-eb5cc8b0026d" width="1280"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[NASA]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[the NASA+ logo against a space background]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[NASA+]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best cameras for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>现在是购买数码相机的奇妙而美好的时机。由于智能手机已经蚕食了休闲摄影市场，制造商正专注于打造专为特定用途而设计的技术奇迹。无反光镜相机在自动对焦、视频等方面不断改进。运动摄像机提供清晰、流畅的视频，紧凑型相机面向游客和视频博主，单反相机的价格是我们见过的最优惠的。然而，数码相机的类型多种多样，您可能需要一些指导才能找到合适的相机，这就是我们的用武之地。多年来，我们测试和审查了数十种无反光镜和数码相机；无论您是正在寻找合适的视频博客相机的创作者、有抱负的野生动物摄影师还是体育爱好者，我们都将帮助您找到适合您的预算和需求的完美相机系统。</p><h2>数码相机购买指南：购买前要考虑什么</h2><h3>传感器</h3><p>选择数码相机而不是智能手机的原因有很多。无反光镜相机中更大的图像传感器可以让更多的光线进入，并且您有多种镜头选择，从广角到长焦再到变焦镜头，具有更优越的光学性能。智能手机只有一个光圈值，而相机有很多光圈值，这可以让您更好地控制曝光。您还可以获得自然的而非人工智能生成的散景、更快的拍摄速度、物理快门、更专业的视频效果等等。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>然而，随着质量的提高，还有许多额外的因素需要考虑。首先是传感器尺寸。一般来说，传感器尺寸越大，相机越好（通常也更贵）。</p><p>全画幅适用于索尼新款 ZV-E1、佳能 EOS R6 II 和松下 S5 II 等型号。它的尺寸相当于 35 毫米胶片 (36 x 24 毫米)，在图像质量、低光能力和景深方面提供最佳性能。它也是最昂贵和最挑剔的。虽然散景在 f/1.4 时看起来令人难以置信，但景深非常薄，以至于拍摄对象的鼻子可能在焦点上，但不是他们的眼睛。这也会给视频拍摄带来困难。 </p><div id="17e6cba906c140a2ad6d0203360809e0"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ESI72hUjqNA?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p>下一个尺寸类别是 APS-C（大多数型号约为 23.5 x 15.6 毫米，佳能约为 22.2 x 14.8 毫米），在富士胶片的 X 系列产品线、佳能的 R10 和 R50 以及尼康 Z50 上提供。无论是相机机身还是镜头，它都比全画幅便宜，但仍然具有大部分优点，如良好的散景、适合低光拍摄的高 ISO 和相对较高的分辨率。它的传感器尺寸与电影摄影机相同，非常适合拍摄视频，并且比全画幅相机更容易保持对焦。</p><p>松下和奥林巴斯共享的微型三分之四 (17.3 x 13mm) 格式是传感器尺寸的下一步缩小。与 APS-C 和全画幅相比，它提供的散景和聚光能力较少，但允许使用更小、更轻的相机和镜头。对于视频，您仍然可以使用优质定焦镜头获得相当紧密的景深，但焦点更容易控制。</p><p>另一种常见的传感器尺寸是 1 型（1 英寸），实际上小于 1 英寸，尺寸为 12.7 x 9.5 毫米。主要用于索尼 ZV-1 视频博客相机等紧凑型机型。最后，GoPro Hero 11 和 DJI Osmo 3 等运动相机的传感器甚至更小（尺寸分别为 1/1.9 和 1/1.7）。</p><h3>自动对焦</h3><p>对于业余和专业摄影师来说，另一个关键因素是出色的自动对焦 (AF) 速度和准确性。大多数现代无反光镜相机都具有混合相位检测自动对焦系统，可实现快速对焦和快速连拍。大多数还具有人工智能智能功能，例如针对人和动物的眼睛检测自动对焦。然而，有些模型只是比其他模型更快一点、反应性更强一些。</p><h3>取景器</h3><p>电子取景器（EVF）和后显示屏也是关键。最好的数码相机拥有最清晰、最明亮的电子取景器，让您在拍摄前最好地判断照片。对于街头摄影之类的事情，最好有尽可能明亮和锐利的后显示屏。您可能还想要一个可以翻转而不仅仅是倾斜的屏幕。</p><h3>镜片</h3><p>数码单反相机和无反光镜相机可以让您更换镜头，但您只能使用紧凑型相机的内置镜头。虽然这对于便携性来说非常有利，但单镜头意味着您将牺牲一些东西。例如，Fujifilm 的 X100V 具有快速但固定的 35mm 等效 f/2.0 镜头，并且没有变焦。索尼的 RX100 V 具有 24-70 毫米变焦，但在长焦端 (f/2.8) 速度较慢，而且清晰度不如定焦镜头。</p><h3>视频功能</h3><p>当谈到视频时，还有其他因素需要考虑。您的相机是否对视频录制进行“像素合并”或读取整个传感器？更好的相机往往会做后者。另一个关键因素是传感器速度，因为较慢的传感器往往有更多的滚动快门，可能会产生使视频倾斜的“果冻”效果。</p><p>另外，电池寿命如何？您喜欢它的操控性和感觉吗？在相机变热或停止之前，您可以拍摄视频多长时间？支持 10 位 HDR 视频吗？有麦克风和/或耳机插孔吗？ （如果您进行大量采访，最好两者都进行。） 视频自动对焦怎么样？所有这些因素都会影响您的决定 - 所以现在让我们来看看现在最好的数码相机。</p><h2>最好的相机</h2><h3>最好的无反光镜相机</h3><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-mirrorless-cameras-133026494.html">无反光镜</a>无疑是当今最大的相机类别，因此如果您想要具有最先进功能的最佳摄影相机，那么无反光镜是最好的选择。佳能和尼康最近都宣布他们将停止开发新的数码单反相机，仅仅是因为该类别的大部分优势都消失了，正如我在<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:YouTube;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=89f68c82-f255-44fa-8db9-03fec996b93a&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=YouTube&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI4OWY2OGM4Mi1mMjU1LTQ0ZmEtOGRiOS0wM2ZlYzk5NmI5M2EiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cueW91dHViZS5jb20vd2F0Y2g_dj1ueVBLQkJlSHk2ayZ0PTFzIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIzNjg0YzFhZS03MTQ1LTRkYzItOWQ4OC0zMGRmZGZlZGFkYTIifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAaSW4adeV86kjVHSaZugxT9y3OFpmPGeYld4L6Wu_zQd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnyPKBBeHy6k%26t%3D1s">最近的视频</a>中详细介绍的那样。无反光镜相机的最大卖点是能够根据您想要进行的拍摄类型更换镜头。</p><p>主要特征是传感器尺寸、分辨率、自动对焦、拍摄速度和视频规格。如果您主要专注于体育摄影或户外摄影，您可能需要快速的拍摄速度和准确的自动对焦。肖像和风景拍摄者可能会青睐大传感器和高分辨率，以最大限度地提高图像质量。内容创作者会希望寻找翻转式显示屏、高端视频规格和良好的体内稳定性等功能。当然，价格也是一个主要因素。</p><h2> 2,000 美元以下的无反光镜相机</h2><h3>2000 美元以下最佳无反光镜相机：佳能 EOS R50</h3><p><core-commerce id="0fcc4f5a6ca94f0cbad34ddc2cb015e8" data-type="product-list"></p><p>我最喜欢的预算相机是佳能全新的 24.2 兆像素<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:B&amp;H Photo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQGNPOAPTjbMo8fI_NOy6A_tkuqZ8i7BBW96k7vQwVHQ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1748810-REG%2Fcanon_eos_r50_mirrorless_camera.html">R50</a> ，它是最好的摄影数码相机之一，内容创作者一定会喜欢它。它可以在电子快门模式下以高达 15 fps 的速度连拍，并以高达 30p 的速度提供 4K 10 位，具有超级采样和无裁剪功能。它有一个完全铰接的显示屏，与这个价格范围内的其他相机不同，它有一个电子取景器。它使用佳能的双像素自动对焦和主体识别模式，甚至还有弹出式闪光灯。唯一的缺点是缺乏像相机本身一样价格实惠的优质镜头，并且缺乏机身稳定性。</p><h3>亚军：佳能EOS R8</h3><p><core-commerce id="a787745eaeb240478f510108eeabb707" data-type="product-list"></p><p>以前全画幅相机的起价通常为 2,000 美元以上，但佳能全新的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAbAei0t33-uU6JuLpkMzHI1ExD4-TvaQaFb7I4kE3eBP&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCanon-Full-Frame-Mirrorless-Lightweight-Smartphone%2Fdp%2FB0BTTTH5G6%3Fth%3D1">EOS R8</a>售价仅为 1,500 美元。它提供佳能出色的双像素自动对焦和人工智能主题识别功能，并能以高达 40 fps 的速度进行连拍。它在视频方面同样强大，支持高达 60 fps 的过采样 10 位 4K。 R8 还提供翻转式显示屏，非常适合视频博主。主要缺点是缺乏体内稳定性。</p><h3>另一个不错的选择：松下 Lumix S5 II</h3><p><core-commerce id="0c4d97c5afa54dbc809d30fa6768ca4c" data-type="product-list"></p><p>内容创作者应该仔细看看<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:B&amp;H Photo;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=95276f3c-7b79-4c1e-803f-981cd9f7a968&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=B%26H+Photo&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXS79eG_Lwa-CBFBcKPyylApACGfhOxX2X-0DGWyUbLc&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bhphotovideo.com%2Fc%2Fproduct%2F1742428-REG%2Fpanasonic_dc_s5m2body_lumix_s5_ii_mirrorless.html">松下的全画幅 S5 II</a> 。这是该公司第一款采用混合相位检测自动对焦的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/panasonic-s5-ii-review-the-full-frame-vlogging-camera-youve-been-waiting-for-150028638.html">相机</a>，旨在使焦点“抖动”和其他问题成为过去。您可以从整个传感器宽度下采样拍摄清晰的 4K 30p 视频，或从 APS-C 裁剪尺寸拍摄 4K 60p 视频，全部采用 10 位颜色。它甚至提供 5.9K 30p 捕捉，以及 RAW 5.9K 外部输出到 Atomos 录音机。您还可以获得用于视频博客的翻转屏幕和业界最佳的更新五轴体内稳定功能。得益于双增益 24 兆像素传感器，照片质量也很好。主要缺点是突发速度较慢。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/panasonic-s5-ii-review-the-full-frame-vlogging-camera-youve-been-waiting-for-150028638.html">阅读我们对松下 Lumix S5 II 的完整评论</a></p><h2>无反光镜相机超过 2,000 美元</h2><h3>2000 美元以上最佳无反光镜相机：索尼 ZV-E1</h3><p><core-commerce id="808f7f977eb7493786e9b9b06fa3d499" data-type="product-list"></p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Tb255LUZ1bGwtRnJhbWUtSW50ZXJjaGFuZ2VhYmxlLU1pcnJvcmxlc3MtQ2FtZXJhL2RwL0IwQlpXTldDWjk_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby11dS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMzY4NGMxYWUtNzE0NS00ZGMyLTlkODgtMzBkZmRmZWRhZGEyIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZTU1q8RvqilGwdTOj2mn_UqxBAeCCaJBZBAoKrWfvvS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Full-Frame-Interchangeable-Mirrorless-Camera%2Fdp%2FB0BZWNWCZ9%3Fth%3D1">索尼 ZV-E1</a>配备与 A7S III 相同的背照式 (BSI) 12 兆像素传感器，提供<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sonys-12-megapixel-full-frame-zv-e1-is-a-low-light-vlogging-beast-140009036.html">出色的低光性能</a>、高达 120p 的 4K 以及自动取景等一系列新的 AI 功能，使其成为摄影和摄像的最佳相机。它还配备了针对视频博主的更新的体内图像稳定（IBIS）系统，可以平滑脚步等震动。 The $2,200 price tag makes it enticing for vloggers as it offers features found on the $3,500 A7S III for considerably less money.</p><h3> Runner up: Fujifilm X-H2S</h3><p><core-commerce id="fd89ed7a9b454a13b0853f1265bb675b" data-type="product-list"></p><p> If you&#39;re OK with a smaller APS-C sensor, check out the <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9GdWppZmlsbS1YLUgyUy1NaXJyb3JsZXNzLUNhbWVyYS1Cb2R5L2RwL0IwQjJGNVZITE0_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tdXUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM2ODRjMWFlLTcxNDUtNGRjMi05ZDg4LTMwZGZkZmVkYWRhMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdI4J0wZt--Z9Pt5jI6_MzXeazc_YkxSPdkpYFzWPFwJ&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFujifilm-X-H2S-Mirrorless-Camera-Body%2Fdp%2FB0B2F5VHLM">Fujifilm X-H2S</a> . It has an incredibly fast stacked, backside-illuminated 26.1-megapixel sensor that allows for rapid burst shooting speeds of 40 fps, along with 4K 120p video with minimal rolling shutter. It can capture ProRes 10-bit video internally, has 7 stops of in-body stabilization and a class-leading EVF. Yes, it&#39;s expensive for an APS-C camera, but on the other hand, it&#39;s the cheapest stacked sensor camera overall. The other downside is AF that&#39;s not quite up to Canon and Sony&#39;s level.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/fujifilm-x-h2s-mirrorless-camera-review-123049866.html">Read our full review of the Fujifilm X-H2S</a></p><h3> Another good option: Sony A7R V</h3><p><core-commerce id="6323f269e5014a62a630b86bfe5bb056" data-type="product-list"></p><p> For the ultimate high-resolution camera, check out <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9Tb255LUZ1bGwtRnJhbWUtTWlycm9ybGVzcy1JbnRlcmNoYW5nZWFibGUtQ2FtZXJhL2RwL0IwQktMUUZGU0Y_dGg9MSZ0YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby11dS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMzY4NGMxYWUtNzE0NS00ZGMyLTlkODgtMzBkZmRmZWRhZGEyIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAVwf83dHGTo3WONrR1FZq3XI4_9vEx31tmFXhxYpZTX8&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Full-Frame-Mirrorless-Interchangeable-Camera%2Fdp%2FB0BKLQFFSF%3Fth%3D1">Sony&#39;s A7R V</a> . With a 61-megapixel sensor, it shoots sharp and beautiful images at a very respectable speed for such a high-resolution model (10 fps). It has an equally fast and reliable autofocus system, the sharpest viewfinder on the market and in-body stabilization that&#39;s much improved over the A7R IV. Video has even improved, with 8K and 10-bit options now on tap, albeit with significant rolling shutter. If you don&#39;t need the video features, however, Sony&#39;s A7R IVa does mostly the same job, photo-wise, and costs a few hundred dollars less.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-a7r-v-review-awesome-images-improved-video-unbeatable-autofocus-150058082.html">Read our full review of the Sony A7R V</a></p><h2> Best action camera</h2><p> The most important features to look for in an action cam are image quality, stabilization and battery life. GoPro has easily been beating all rivals over the last few years in all those areas, but DJI made some strides last year with the Osmo Action 3. At the same time, GoPro&#39;s latest models are more expensive than rivals.</p><h3> Best action camera: GoPro Hero 11 Black</h3><p><core-commerce id="6c030b4e0a724884b6ea95512376ff9d" data-type="product-list"></p><p> GoPro didn&#39;t change the design on its latest model, but it has a larger sensor that enables a couple of cool features – Horizon Lock stabilization and Full Frame mode that makes it easier to shoot for, say, TikTok and YouTube at the same time. It also offers a new wider, though slightly distorted Hyperview field of view.</p><p> Otherwise, the <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:GoPro;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=06fa1f29-e83c-49e4-81a8-9732450da8a9&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=GoPro&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQxGXJQH_IppkyCdZjAB32vthp2txOLVTmKYXpTnYRrS&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fgopro.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Fshop%2Fcameras%2Fhero11-black%2FCHDHX-111-master.html">Hero 11 Black</a> offers better video quality than ever (up to 5.3K 60p), Hypersmooth stabilization that&#39;s still the best in the business (by far), battery life that&#39;s improved by 40 percent over the last model, and more. It&#39;s easily the best action camera on the market, but you pay for that: it&#39;s $400 with a one year subscription ($500 without it), compared to $329 for the DJI Osmo Action 3 and $300 for the Insta360 RS 4K bundle. If you&#39;re serious about filming extreme sports, though, it&#39;s worth it.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/gopro-hero-11-review-125905853.html">Read our full review of the GoPro Hero 11</a></p><h3> Runner up: DJI Osmo Action 3</h3><p><core-commerce id="42d2cf364079470392365a559708f0a0" data-type="product-list"></p><p> After experimenting with an oddball modular design on the Action 2, design has gone back to a more classic action cam design on the <a data-i13n="cpos:16;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ESkktU3VwZXItV2lkZS1Ib3Jpem9uU3RlYWR5LVdhdGVycHJvb2YtTG9uZy1MYXN0aW5nL2RwL0IwQjdYMkxYUTY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tdXUtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM2ODRjMWFlLTcxNDUtNGRjMi05ZDg4LTMwZGZkZmVkYWRhMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfCLlzGupjmaFNj3gORx9vZ6hl-uM421pYSWosTHwFIx&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FDJI-Super-Wide-HorizonSteady-Waterproof-Long-Lasting%2Fdp%2FB0B7X2LXQ6">Osmo Action 3</a> . It also comes with a slick new magnetic quick-release mount that lets you connect the camera directly to a GoPro-style mount with or without the case. Video quality and stabilization are quite good, but fall short of the Hero 11 Black (the Action 3 tops out at 4K 120p resolution compared to 5.3K 60p on the GoPro). While it&#39;s not quite as good as the Hero 11, it&#39;s considerably cheaper.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/dji-osmo-action-3-far-more-battery-life-fast-charging-and-a-spiffy-new-mount-120035233.html">Read our full review of the DJI Osmo Action 3</a></p><h2> Best compact camera</h2><p> This category has fewer cameras than it did even a few years ago and many models are older, as manufacturers focus instead on mirrorless models. However, I&#39;m still a big believer in compact cameras. This type of camera is a big step up from smartphones quality-wise, and a lot of people will take a compact traveling or to events when they&#39;d never bother with the hassle of a DSLR or mirrorless camera.</p><p> Compacts largely have type 1-inch sensors, but a few offer larger options, particularly Fujifilm&#39;s XF-100V. Another popular model, Sony&#39;s XV-1, is primarily aimed at content creators looking to step up. In any case, desirable qualities include image quality, a fast lens, relatively long zoom, flip-out display, good battery life, a high quality EVF, decent video and good pocketability.</p><h3> Best compact camera: Fujifilm X100V</h3><p><core-commerce id="92f4461aa31f4807b9b9d196a69e2c94" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Adorama;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=0eee6f60-6f21-4ba6-b70e-cc15b39bf860&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Adorama&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiIwZWVlNmY2MC02ZjIxLTRiYTYtYjcwZS1jYzE1YjM5YmY4NjAiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYWRvcmFtYS5jb20vaWZqeDEwMHZzLmh0bWwiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjM2ODRjMWFlLTcxNDUtNGRjMi05ZDg4LTMwZGZkZmVkYWRhMiJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAbZrABxIdUjxo2_QKkiEyqsbIKzN_vVi5pbbI4KJYg3n&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adorama.com%2Fifjx100vs.html">X100V</a> is the latest in Fujifilm&#39;s famous fixed-lens X100 camera series. Like other models in the lineup, it has an APS-C sensor and a 23mm f/2.0 lens, equivalent to 35mm on a full-frame sensor. You also get the same hybrid optical/electronic viewfinder, mechanical dials, film simulations and good looks as before. But the X100V is the most significant advancement in the series&#39; history. It has Fujifilm&#39;s latest 26.1-megapixel X-Trans 4 CMOS sensor compared to 24.2-megapixels on the last model and a new, sharper lens to handle that extra resolution.</p><p> A new tilting rear display makes &quot;shooting from the hip&quot; street photography much easier, as does the fast 11 fps/20 fps shooting speeds in mechanical/silent shutter modes. You also get a better hybrid phase- and contrast-detect autofocus (AF) system with more AF points along with face and eye detection. Finally, it now has the same 4K video-shooting features as the X-T30. It doesn&#39;t come cheap, but the X100V is the ultimate camera if you&#39;re into street photography – assuming you can <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.dpreview.com/forums/thread/4695587">find one</a> .</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-03-24-fujifilm-x100v-compact-camera-review.html">Read our full review of the Fujifilm X100V</a></p><h3> Runner up: Sony ZV-1</h3><p><core-commerce id="29d538fa485747f8b79db21757ef7d58" data-type="product-list"></p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:21;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAaWp66eHqX1HYzlVjbEpsDrBC9YQpv-LJNpm4HH_FbKt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSony-Content-Creators-Vlogging-Microphone%2Fdp%2FB08965JV8D%3Fth%3D1">ZV-1</a> is Sony&#39;s first RX100-series camera designed specifically for vlogging. It does that job well thanks to a lightweight body, built-in high-quality microphone, flip-out display, best-in-class autofocus and excellent image quality. The 24-70mm lens is sharp, but it needs to be wider because of the 25 percent crop when using electronic stabilization. It also lacks a true touch display and a headphone port. That nitpicking aside, if you&#39;re looking to step up from a smartphone or just want something simple, it does the job nearly perfectly.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:22;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sony-zv-1-vlogging-camera-review-162822651.html">Read our full review of the Sony ZV-1</a></p><h3> Another good option: Panasonic ZS-200</h3><p><core-commerce id="833d101b29c24d6a94cd943ab7b81b5f" data-type="product-list"></p><p> For a value compact camera, the best option is Panasonic&#39;s 20-megapixel <a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUezUfxPy2h-trf4jyr95QCSAAv0yL6EO77foAFnUdtj&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FPANASONIC-Stabilization-Megapixel-Sensor-DC-ZS200S%2Fdp%2FB079QNXFCC%3Fth%3D1">ZS-200</a> . It offers a lot of features for the price, like a 1-inch, 20.1 megapixel sensor, 5-axis stabilization, 4K, 30 fps video and more. Its main claim to fame, though, is the 24-360x lens that offers incredible reach for travel and more. Though it dates back to 2018, it&#39;s actually one of the more recent compact models.</p><h2> Best DSLR camera</h2><p> With mirrorless cameras taking over the interchangeable lens market, DSLRs still give you the ability to change lenses at relatively cheap prices. The defining feature is the reflex mirror that lets you look directly through the lens at your subject with no electronics in between. Most also have very fast autofocus thanks to a dedicated phase-detect sensor, and very fast battery life. However, many lack features you&#39;d expect on modern mirrorless cameras like subject tracking, eye-detection and more.</p><h3> Best DSLR camera: Nikon D850</h3><p><core-commerce id="13aeb905f00642c09cb5661564f8ebeb" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Nikon&#39;s full-frame (FX) <a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASKBTK1v7wIk9EBRLRFgcu_J1t23aEedlVLba83Si1V0&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FNikon-D850-FX-Format-Digital-Camera%2Fdp%2FB07524LHMT%3Fth%3D1">D850</a> is the best deal on a high-end camera and arguably the best camera for photography. With a 45.7-megapixel sensor and max 102,400 ISO, it gives you the best quality for the money, whether mirrorless or DSLR. It can also shoot fast, at up to 7fps, which is very good for such a high-res camera. In addition, the battery life (1840 shots on a charge) puts any mirrorless option to shame, and there&#39;s a massive number of FX Nikkor lens options to choose from. Nikon has upped its video game as well with the D850 by introducing 4K internal recording. If you&#39;d still rather have a live optical rather than an electronic view, the D850 is the best option available.</p><h3> Runner up: Canon EOS Rebel SL3</h3><p><core-commerce id="e341516cb4374770afb8e580d860eec7" data-type="product-list"></p><p> Another one of the best cameras for photography is Canon&#39;s 24-megapixel APS-C <a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASwImYIK8e5-fOTXlj2rbEEcYAUK69jT9uXLtHPplmJv&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FCanon-Rebel-18-55mm-Lens-White%2Fdp%2FB07QHPT781%3Fth%3D1">EOS Rebel SL3</a> , which has a great blend of features, build quality and value. It offers features like a vari-angle touchscreen, 4K video (albeit with a crop) and Dual Pixel autofocus technology in live mode. You get shooting speeds of up to 5 fps, 1600 shots on a charge and an ISO range up to 51,200 (expanded). It also offers guided screen options, making it one of the best cameras for beginners. Best of all, it offers excellent picture quality for the price thanks to Canon&#39;s skin-friendly color science.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-cameras-151524327.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3684c1ae-7145-4dc2-9d88-30dfdfedada2</guid><dc:creator> Steve Dent</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 14:05:07 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1698933907</ingested><modified> 2023-11-02T14:05:23+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Cameras & Photography]]></category><category><![CDATA[Shopping]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1238" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-02/cb39b890-b2f6-11ed-afff-4d399c6315d8" width="2200"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:tit